{
  "id": "2652767974_2",
  "title": "佩通坦，绝地翻盘还是彻底下台？",
  "content": "<div class=\"rich_media_content js_underline_content autoTypeSetting24psection\" id=\"js_content\">\n <section data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n  <span leaf=\"\">\n   <img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"505244356\" data-ratio=\"0.09259259259259259\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"/static/res/logo/https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/BIH6m4FJcJkk0zxaFtDkTic4ql3NJrddcQGalJpCTKAzwe3Kfzzmc5mmmHBkf28BE1WursGvzq4ySSLOXwJSiaxQ/640?wx_fmt=other&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;wx_co=1&amp;tp=webp\" style=\"font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;text-align: center;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible !important;width: 1080px !important;\"/>\n  </span>\n  <span leaf=\"\">\n   <br/>\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section data-role=\"paragraph\">\n  <section data-autoskip=\"1\">\n   <section data-mpa-action-id=\"mco3dywevnj\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <section style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px;\">\n     <span data-mpa-action-id=\"mc8z9x2s1xmt\" leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <br/>\n     </span>\n    </section>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span data-mpa-action-id=\"mco3dyuxnn9\" leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n       执政未满一年，泰国史上最年轻的总理佩通坦，正面临政治生涯中最严峻的一次挑战。\n      </span>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <br/>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n       “录音事件使得泰国内部原本存在的各种对立或分歧，一下子爆发出来，佩通坦继续担任总理的可能性并不大。”中国国际问题研究院国际战略研究所副研究员唐奇芳在接受中新网记者采访时指出。\n      </span>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <br/>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <section nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n     <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"505284296\" data-ratio=\"0.6655913978494624\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"930\" src=\"/static/res/logo/https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/BIH6m4FJcJn04lHzLpp07lOVkUibpIm2pnm4f4oM7hMha9AaDnEZQcay1DrPLRK8Fg7EEH8msC7dFVsgZcAbJEQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" type=\"block\"/>\n    </section>\n    <p data-mpa-action-id=\"mco3ekwd1rrq\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" mpa-font-style=\"mco3ekvv217y\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;font-size: 12px;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"\">\n      <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\" textstyle=\"\">\n       当地时间2025年7月1日，泰国总理府，佩通坦在被泰国宪法法院停职后举行记者会。图/视觉中国\n      </span>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <br/>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p data-mpa-action-id=\"mco3eol61n4\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" mpa-font-style=\"mco3eokm6l9\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;font-size: 17px;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"\">\n      <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(0, 122, 170);font-weight: bold;\" textstyle=\"\">\n       录音事件，打开“潘多拉魔盒”\n      </span>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <br/>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n       泰国宪法法院7月1日宣布，受理有关调查总理佩通坦是否存在违宪行为的请愿书，并决定即日起暂停佩通坦行使总理职权，泰国政坛再生波澜。\n      </span>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <br/>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n       而这一切的导火索，是一段电话录音。\n      </span>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <br/>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n       6月18日，柬埔寨方面流出一段佩通坦和柬埔寨参议院主席洪森的通话录音，引发巨大争议。泰国执政联盟第二大党自豪泰党宣布退出执政联盟，其党首、副总理兼内政部长阿努廷等多名自豪泰党内阁成员辞职。\n      </span>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <br/>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n       佩通坦很快对此道歉，但风波仍持续发酵。\n      </span>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <br/>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n       6月28日，大批反对者在曼谷市中心举行大规模集会，要求佩通坦下台。这位年轻女总理的支持率，也暴跌至9.2%。\n      </span>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <br/>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n       唐奇芳指出，录音事件好似“打开了潘多拉魔盒”，引发了一系列反应。\n      </span>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <br/>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n       “而此事发生的深层原因，最主要的还是泰国不同的政治力量之间长期斗争和矛盾爆发的结果。”唐奇芳说。\n      </span>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <br/>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n       唐奇芳认为，目前泰国的执政联盟“危如累卵”，录音事件使得2024年8月以来达到的脆弱平衡开始崩溃，泰国内部的各种对立和分歧，一下子全部爆发出来。\n      </span>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <br/>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;font-size: 17px;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\">\n      <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(0, 122, 170);font-weight: bold;\" textstyle=\"\">\n       保住总理之位，并非当务之急\n      </span>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <br/>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n       遭到暂时停职后，佩通坦当天表示，将在宪法法院规定的15天内，准备好辩护材料，并称将在停职期间将继续为国家工作。\n      </span>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <br/>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n       佩通坦能否挺过这一关？\n      </span>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <br/>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n       唐奇芳从两个角度进行了分析。\n      </span>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <br/>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n       首先，从执政联盟内部看，由于自豪泰党已宣布退出执政联盟，议会席位减少，而联盟内部出现分裂迹象，各党已经开始动摇。\n      </span>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <br/>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n       另一方面，根据泰国最新民调，为泰党的支持率仅有10%左右，而反对党人民党超过40%。民意对为泰党十分不利。\n      </span>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <br/>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n       由此，唐奇芳认为，“如果佩通坦想辩护成功继续担任总理，难度会非常大，这种可能性并不高。”\n      </span>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <br/>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n       “佩通坦的当务之急，是思考如何采取有效手段，保住为泰党以及自己将来从政的空间和前途。”唐奇芳表示。\n      </span>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <br/>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n       她进一步说，“佩通坦能否继续担任总理并非最重要的，如何在一定程度上，挽回民众对为泰党、包括西那瓦家族的好感或支持，不要让目前的不利情况进一步恶化，才最重要。”\n      </span>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <br/>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;font-size: 17px;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\">\n      <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(0, 122, 170);font-weight: bold;\" textstyle=\"\">\n       未来泰国政局，可能有哪些走向？\n      </span>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <br/>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n       新加坡《联合早报》称，佩通坦和其执政联盟未来的不确定性，影响了泰国政局的稳定性，以及政府促进经济增长的努力。\n      </span>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <br/>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n       沉重压力之下，他信家族的政治命运再次陷入扑朔迷离的状态。\n      </span>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <br/>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <section nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n     <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"505284295\" data-ratio=\"0.6654320987654321\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"810\" src=\"/static/res/logo/https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/BIH6m4FJcJn04lHzLpp07lOVkUibpIm2p10vusr1F935PZMocibpNao0sFMUxQPwXicu2IJcAkxfq2E1XG5wN3d7Q/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" type=\"block\"/>\n    </section>\n    <p data-mpa-action-id=\"mco3f3o222o3\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" mpa-font-style=\"mco3f3nn565\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;font-size: 12px;text-align: center;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"\">\n      <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\" textstyle=\"\">\n       资料图：泰国前总理他信。\n      </span>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <br/>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n       “此次事件严重冲击了他信家族，使其元气大伤。”唐奇芳说道。\n      </span>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <br/>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n       唐奇芳表示，“近20年来，为泰党在整个泰国政治中，是最重要的政治力量之一，他信家族也是最有影响的一个政治家族。但随着泰国社会和政治的变化，为泰党的执政基础，也随着时间流逝不断削弱。”\n      </span>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <br/>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n       在她看来，\n      </span>\n      <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\" textstyle=\"\">\n       佩通坦继续担任总理的可能性非常小\n      </span>\n      <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n       ，而泰国政局，也随之迎来两种走向。\n      </span>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <br/>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\" textstyle=\"\">\n       第一，不提前大选，维持目前的执政联盟。\n      </span>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <br/>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n       唐奇芳说，如果不提前大选，不解散下议院，维持现在的以为泰党为首的执政联盟的话，为泰党将提名新的总理人选。\n      </span>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <br/>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\" textstyle=\"\">\n       第二，解散下议院，提前举行大选。\n      </span>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <br/>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n       如果佩通坦下台后，很快举行大选，唐奇芳表示，按照目前的民意，结果会对为泰党不利。风头正盛的人民党，很有可能组阁。\n      </span>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <br/>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span data-mpa-action-id=\"mco3dyux1ypp\" leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n      <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n       “佩通坦的政治前途很可能在两个月内终结。”新加坡《联合早报》援引泰国政治学家的话称。与此同时，舆论认为，目前泰国低迷的经济，恐怕承受不起这场政治巨变。\n      </span>\n     </span>\n    </p>\n    <section style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n     <span style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">\n     </span>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n </section>\n <section class=\"mp_profile_iframe_wrp\" nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n  <mp-common-profile class=\"js_uneditable custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe\" data-alias=\"cns2012\" data-from=\"2\" data-headimg=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/BIH6m4FJcJn8Frnv2d6HqFTpU77JE2D2mOhC8djIhibX35b1MZIbBNh12ib2ELEia2SqjDcefqicFl2KjiaXEGoBQGA/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-id=\"MjM5ODA4OTIyMA==\" data-is_biz_ban=\"0\" data-nickname=\"中国新闻网\" data-pluginname=\"mpprofile\" data-servic